#############################################################################
########################     EvoBB 0.2r1  ###################################
#############################################################################

This update is very very minor, but i felt it should be done, as it makes 
it all a little 'neater'.
Basically, it includes:
	- A fix for the tables in deletetopic.php(3).
	- New feature: You can now delete individual posts from a topic.
		This is done by the trashcan icon by the posters name.
	- Performance enhancements in viewtopic.php(3).

To update just simply replace the given files here, with the ones on your
webserver.

Enjoy :)

- The EvoBB team.